From: Madhvapathi Sriram <sriram.m@ti.com>
Date: Thu, 13 Jan 2011 16:27:45 +0530
Subject: [PATCH 284/609] video: da8xxfb.c: Corrected the da8xx FB parameters
 for da850/omap-l138

Original commit: e0dba0179d887b2d47c1c64b02ce4ef0d407a401

  From git://arago-project.org/git/projects/linux-am33x.git
  And ti-sdk-am335x-evm-05.05.00.00-Linux-x86-Install image

The vfp and the vbp parameters were needed to be modified for
LK043T1DG01 display panel. Without this modification, the first
line would be cropped and not be visible on the display.

Signed-off-by: Madhvapathi Sriram <sriram.m@ti.com>
Signed-off-by: Vaibhav Hiremath <hvaibhav@ti.com>
---
 drivers/video/da8xx-fb.c |    4 ++--
 1 files changed, 2 insertions(+), 2 deletions(-)

diff --git a/drivers/video/da8xx-fb.c b/drivers/video/da8xx-fb.c
index b9fd183..c1393a3 100644
--- a/drivers/video/da8xx-fb.c
+++ b/drivers/video/da8xx-fb.c
@@ -235,8 +235,8 @@ static struct da8xx_panel known_lcd_panels[] = {
 		.hfp = 2,
 		.hbp = 2,
 		.hsw = 41,
-		.vfp = 2,
-		.vbp = 2,
+		.vfp = 3,
+		.vbp = 3,
 		.vsw = 10,
 		.pxl_clk = 7833600,
 		.invert_pxl_clk = 0,
